From: Joel Selvaraj <foss@joelselvaraj.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Jun 2025 22:44:00 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 082/194] stalled! arm64: dts: qcom: sdm845-shift-axolotl: Add
 q6voicedai reg

This makes it similar to the other dais. Noticed in sdm660 repo.  But I am not sure if it's a functional requirement. Anyways let's specify it.

Signed-off-by: Joel Selvaraj <foss@joelselvaraj.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sdm845-shift-axolotl.dts | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sdm845-shift-axolotl.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sdm845-shift-axolotl.dts
index 9eae07cb7e91..38c7fa966324 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sdm845-shift-axolotl.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sdm845-shift-axolotl.dts
@@ -743,6 +743,12 @@
 	};
 };
 
+&q6voicedai {
+	dai@1 {
+		reg = <VOICEMMODE1>;
+	};
+};
+
 &qup_uart9_rx {
 	drive-strength = <2>;
 	bias-pull-up;
-- 
